nerals-janazat","tag-graves","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-sadness-al-huzn","tag-weeping-al-baka"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9fi","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":35188,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/09\/recite-then-weep\/","url_meta":{"origin":35544,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tilawah: Recite the Quran pleasantly, then cry over it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 9, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, this Quran has descended with sadness. If you recite it, then weep. If you cannot weep, then feign weeping. Recite in a melodious tone, for whoever does not use a pleasant voice is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/why-servants-despair\/","url_meta":{"origin":35544,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Laughter: Why make My servants despair?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to a group of his companions while they were laughing and talking. The Prophet said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is my soul, if you knew what I knew, you would laugh little and weep often.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35276,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/20\/special-place-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35544,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ostentation: Special place in Hell for reciters showing off","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from the pit of sorrow.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the pit of sorrow?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is a valley in Hell from which Hell itself seeks refuge\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5503,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/24\/qabr-first-stage-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35544,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Qabr: Grave is first stage of the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Uthman reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the grave is the first stage of the Hereafter. If one is saved from it, whatever comes after will be easier for him. If one is not saved from it, whatever comes after will be harder for him.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38808,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/16\/wailing-makruh\/","url_meta":{"origin":35544,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Angels prod those who wail over his grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa al-Ash\u2019ari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo person dies and people stand over him wailing, saying, \u2018What a great man he was! How dignified he was!\u2019 but that two angels are appointed over him to prod him, saying, \u2018Is that really\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36293,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/23\/guarding-weeping-lowering-gaze\/","url_meta":{"origin":35544,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Eyes: Guarding, weeping, and lowering gaze","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Jaydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThree eyes will never see the Hellfire, an eye standing guard in the way of Allah, an eye weeping from the fear of Allah, and an eye lowering its gaze from what Allah has forbidden.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35544","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abua